      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me! It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and honestly just a total joy to drive. I've taken great care of it, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It\u2019s got plenty of life left and looks fantastic in the driveway\u2014perfect for your next adventure. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
