    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been properly sorted with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical components are dialed in for peak performance, offering the tactile feedback and linear power delivery characteristic of this legendary platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
