    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of a well-maintained daily driver. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep shine, showing only minor, superficial stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is free of tears, and all electronic features\u2014from the infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision, backed by a consistent service history and a recent multi-point inspection. This car offers a reliable, comfortable driving experience for someone looking for quality and longevity without the 'new car' price tag.",
