    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been a fantastic car for me and is still in really solid shape. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the maintenance, so it runs smoothly and is super reliable for whatever adventures you have planned. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is honestly just a joy to drive. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to message me with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 32000.0,
