    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) powered by the legendary S65B40 naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant features individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering linear torque through a 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity has been prioritized: the critical rod bearing service and throttle valve actuators have been completed as preventative measures. The chassis features Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and a Variable M Differential Lock for superior lateral dynamics. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the subframe and suspension bushings remain tight, and the engine exhibits excellent compression. A true mechanical specimen for the purist.",
